---
// About component: Personal story with credibility signals
---

<section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading" class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6">
  <div class="container max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 id="about-heading" class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-text-light dark:text-text-dark">
      About Joel
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-8 items-start">
      <!-- Image column -->
      <figure class="border-[4px] border-text-light dark:border-text-dark bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 shadow-neo-yellow aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src="/images/selfie.jpg"
          alt="Joel Shinness"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </figure>

      <!-- Content column -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Credibility stats - prominent display -->
        <div class="flex gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-text">10+</span>
            <span class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">Years Experience</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <span class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-text">50+</span>
            <span class="font-body text-sm text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">Projects Delivered</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Narrative paragraphs -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-text-light dark:text-text-dark">
            I've been building custom software for small businesses for over 10 years, working with more than 50 clients to solve problems that off-the-shelf tools can't handle.
          </p>

          <p class="font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-text-light dark:text-text-dark">
            I focus on helping businesses get exactly what they need without the enterprise price tag. Whether it's a custom web app, automating tedious workflows, or adding AI features to your product.
          </p>

          <p class="font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-text-light dark:text-text-dark">
            When I'm not coding, you'll find me exploring new technologies, mentoring developers, and enjoying outdoor adventures with my family.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
